                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">No. 22.</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Earl Russell</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Mason</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Foreign Office,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1863-10-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 6, 1863.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Lord Russell presents his compliments to Mr. Mason, and has the honor to
                    acknowledge the receipt of his note of the 28th ultimo, enclosing certain
                    original papers relating to the case of the vessel Margaret and Jessie.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
